=== 古希臘 ===
{{Main|古希臘宗教}}

在古希臘的[[奧林匹斯十二主神|奧林匹斯十二主神]]分別為：<ref name="EnAm1993">{{Cite encyclopedia |title=Greek mythology |encyclopedia=[[Encyclopedia_Americana|Encyclopedia Americana]] |year=1993 |volume=13 |page=431}}</ref><ref name="EnPLB2007">{{cite encyclopedia |title=Dodekatheon |trans_title=Twelve Olympians |encyclopedia=Papyrus Larousse Britannica |year=2007 |language=el}}</ref> [[宙斯|宙斯]]，[[赫拉|赫拉]]，[[波塞冬|波塞冬]]，[[雅典娜|雅典娜]]，[[阿瑞斯|阿瑞斯]]，[[得墨忒耳|得墨忒耳]]，[[阿波羅|阿波羅]]，[[阿耳忒彌斯|阿耳忒彌斯]]，[[赫淮斯托斯|赫淮斯托斯]]，[[阿佛洛狄忒|阿佛洛狄忒]]，[[赫耳墨斯|赫耳墨斯]]和[[赫斯提亞|赫斯提亞]]。赫斯提亞下台後[[狄俄尼索斯|狄俄尼索斯]]被邀請到[[奧林匹斯山|奧林匹斯山]]，這是一個有爭議的問題。羅伯特格雷夫斯的「希臘神話」建議赫斯提亞交出她的座位，但他援引的兩個來源<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.perseus.tufts.edu/hopper/text?doc=Apollod.+3.5.3&fromdoc=Perseus%3Atext%3A1999.01.0022|title=Apollodorus, Library Sir James George Frazer, Ed.|language=en|accessdate=2014-03-26|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112211719/http://www.perseus.tufts.edu/hopper/text?doc=Apollod.+3.5.3&fromdoc=Perseus%3Atext%3A1999.01.0022|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.perseus.tufts.edu/hopper/text?doc=Paus.+2.31.2&fromdoc=Perseus%3Atext%3A1999.01.0160|title=Pausanias, Description of Greece|language=en|accessdate=2014-03-26|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112211721/http://www.perseus.tufts.edu/hopper/text?doc=Paus.+2.31.2&fromdoc=Perseus%3Atext%3A1999.01.0160|dead-url=no}}</ref>顯然不建議赫斯提亞這樣做。[[哈迪斯|哈迪斯]]<ref name="EnAm1919">{{cite encyclopedia |title=Encyclopedia Americana Vol. 13 |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=PWYMAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA408 |volume=13 |year=1919 |editor=George Edward Rines |publisher=Americana Corp |pages=408–411 |access-date=2013-07-12 |archive-date=2020-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200206062703/https://books.google.com/books?id=PWYMAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA408 |dead-url=no }}</ref>會因為他住在陰間而不包括在奧林匹斯十二主神內。所有的神都有一種能力。

==民間信仰==
{{Main|民間信仰}}
現今所謂的[[民間信仰|民間信仰]]（不是指傳統的[[民族宗教|民族宗教]]）主要是在[[亚太地区|亚太地区]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.pewforum.org/2012/12/18/global-religious-landscape-folk/ |title=Folk Religionists |author=<!--Not stated--> |date=2012-12-18 |website=Pew Forum |publisher=Pew Research Center |access-date=2021-03-31 |archive-date=2018-10-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181003215140/http://www.pewforum.org/2012/12/18/global-religious-landscape-folk/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此一事實反映了有許多多神教都是出現在西方世界以外的事實<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Gries |first1=P. |last2=Su |first2=J. |last3=Schak |first3=D. |date=December 2012 |title=Toward the scientific study of polytheism: beyond forced‐choice measures of religious belief |url=https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1111/j.1468-5906.2012.01683.x |journal=Journal for the Scientific Study of Religion |volume=51 |issue=4 |pages=623–637 |doi=10.1111/j.1468-5906.2012.01683.x |access-date=2021-03-31 |archive-date=2021-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210415205344/https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1111/j.1468-5906.2012.01683.x |dead-url=no }}</ref>

民間信仰和[[泛靈論|泛靈論]]有密切關係。在古代文化或是現在的文化中，都還是有泛靈論的信仰。若是在一神論的社會中，會將民間信仰視為是迷信<ref name="van Baaren">{{cite web |url=https://www.britannica.com/topic/monotheism/The-spectrum-of-views-monotheisms-and-quasi-monotheisms |title=Monotheism |last=van Baaren |first=Theodorus P. |website=Britannica |publisher=Encyclopaedia Britannica |access-date=2021-04-12 |archive-date=2021-05-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210514112933/https://www.britannica.com/topic/monotheism/The-spectrum-of-views-monotheisms-and-quasi-monotheisms |dead-url=no }}</ref>。民間信仰可能沒有有組織的[[圣职者|圣职者]]，也沒有正式的[[宗教經典|宗教經典]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.pewforum.org/2012/12/18/global-religious-landscape-folk/ |title=Folk Religionists |author=<!--Not stated--> |date=2012-12-18 |website=Pew Forum |publisher=Pew Research Center |access-date=2021-03-31 |archive-date=2018-10-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181003215140/http://www.pewforum.org/2012/12/18/global-religious-landscape-folk/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。民間信仰也可能和其他的宗教信仰一起出現。西方世界是以[[亞伯拉罕諸教|亞伯拉罕諸教]]為主，是一神論的宗教，不接受同時信奉多個宗教，但在民間信仰中，可能會有同時信奉多個民間信仰神明的情形<ref name="van Baaren"/>。
